title: Catching The Impossible - All 9 Episodes
description:
This is the entire series of what has been described as the best angling movies ever made.

The first three episodes started off as the 700mb rips uploaded here by Nicuscarpe. The 1st one had a weird aspect ratio and played back in 4:3 ratio so everything was tall and skinny. I've modified this so it plays back properly in 16:9 ratio. The 2nd and 3rd files are unmodified so if you already have these you can just rename them and put them in this download directory.

Episodes 4 to 9 were the 2.2gb rips uploaded by Poepzooi, some of them from here and the rest from other sites. I've re-encoded them all to 700mb rips to create a more reasonable file size without undue loss of quality. I hope I've done a decent job. All files have been checked for audio sync and everything looks good.

Enjoy.
